room_title: Escape room "Santa’s List" by Lock and Key Escape in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description: Santa has added your name to his naughty list by mistake. You and your team have to travel to Santa’s workshop to solve this problem. Santa keeps the list under lock and key, and you only have 60 minutes to find the list before Santa returns. If you are caught, your name will be permanently added to the naughty list forever. See if your family has what it takes to make it back into Santa’s good graces this year.
